/// Row-level security: members of this role see only Artemis-3 rows. Demonstrates
/// governance carried all the way to the report layer. In the Service: model -> Security,
/// assign members; or Modeling -> View as -> this role to test. Add more roles (one per
/// program) or make it dynamic with USERPRINCIPALNAME() against a user->program table.
role 'Artemis-3 Analyst'
	modelPermission: read

	tablePermission artemis_supply_risk = 'artemis_supply_risk'[program] = "Artemis-3"

	annotation PBI_Id = 4b8d9ebdd80b421a91b2709c17c167b1

